\insrsid8942813\charrsid11886030 didn\rquote t}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3500228\charrsid11886030  get anything much the matter with us did we?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13566012 OF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8942813\charrsid11886030  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3500228\charrsid11886030 No}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8942813\charrsid11886030  

