 colds but - nobody made a fuss of illness did they?}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8942813\charrsid11886030  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3500228\charrsid11886030 
