\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13566012 OF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3500228\charrsid11886030 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15401715 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3500228\charrsid11886030 Was there anything like wild duck or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13566012 OF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3500228\charrsid11886030 Well, no - no, not wild duck. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15401715 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3500228\charrsid11886030 Were you allowed to talk during meals or not?
