\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15401715 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3500228\charrsid11886030 This was a bit unusual for a Victorian family was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13566012 OF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3500228\charrsid11886030 Yes, it was a bit. Yes, some people thought that children should be seen and not heard. But there was none of that about our house, no.

