\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15401715 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3500228\charrsid11886030 No, I don't think so, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13566012 OF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3500228\charrsid11886030 No.
